channel.title: My own sword design!
channel.description:

So i drew this and thought it actually looked kinda cool! and made a model out of it to see how it will turn out. Also thanks amy for showing me the right way to color! item.title: My own sword design!
item.dc:creator: @amy_webb1 amy_webb
item.description:
@amy_webb1 wrote:

Nice design, however your wireframe is still a little messy. It is better but you still have a few places to improve on, i’ve drawn you a wireframe from your picture so you can get a general idea. It looks a little messy in some places but i was trying to stick to your drawing, places like the little teeth of the model i would have lined up directly with the middle of the blade so it looked neater.

Your handle was pretty much on spot, it was just the blade you need to work on. Was still a very nice model, i can see you added shades of model which is nice.
